      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      651.97,
      526.39,
      665.01
    ],
    "text": "imprisonment in default. Further, compensation of Rs. 300,000/- was ordered to be paid",
