      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      671.77,
      526.49,
      684.81
    ],
    "text": "to each of the victims; in default, a term of 6 months of rigorous imprisonment was",
