      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      691.69,
      376.22,
      704.73
    ],
    "text": "imposed, and the appellant was acquitted of the 3rd count.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      723.49,
      526.41,
      736.53
    ],
    "text": "Being aggrieved by the aforementioned conviction and the sentence, the Accused has",
