      72.02,
      71.91,
      526.37,
      84.95
    ],
    "text": "When the matter was argued on 27.01.2026, the Learned Counsel called upon the Accused",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      91.73,
      526.49,
      104.77
    ],
    "text": "to move to withdraw the Appeal against the conviction and canvass only the sentence, on",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      111.65,
      526.35,
      124.69
    ],
    "text": "the basis that the Learned High Court Judge had failed to consider the mitigatory factors",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      131.45,
      221.76,
      144.49
    ],
    "text": "when imposing the sentence.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      163.25,
      526.11,
      176.29
    ],
    "text": "It is well established that, in the process of sentencing, Courts are required to take into",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      183.05,
      526.23,
      196.09
    ],
    "text": "account both aggravating and mitigating circumstances, together with the gravity of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      202.97,
      526.39,
      216.01
    ],
    "text": "offence. At the stage of inquiry preceding the imposition of sentence, the Counsel for the",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      222.77,
      365.66,
      235.81
    ],
    "text": "Prosecution pleaded the following factors as aggravating:",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      254.57,
      526.47,
      267.78
    ],
    "text": "1. At the time of the offence victims were 7 years old, and the Appellant was 27 years",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      274.52,
      129.45,
      287.56
    ],
    "text": "old.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      294.32,
      505.25,
      307.53
    ],
    "text": "2. The Appellant was a neighbour of the victims, thereby occupying a position of",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      314.12,
      243.48,
      327.16
    ],
    "text": "proximity and familiarity.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      346.04,
      526.32,
      359.08
    ],
    "text": "Further, before sentencing, the Counsel for the Appellant pleaded the following factors as",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      365.84,
      137.61,
      378.88
    ],
    "text": "mitigating:",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      391.64,
      356.9,
      404.85
    ],
    "text": "1. The Appellant is unmarried and 41 years of age.",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      411.56,
      526.25,
      424.9
    ],
    "text": "2. His occupation is that of a three\u2011wheeler driver, which is his sole means of",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "CambriaMath",
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      431.36,
      163.41,
      444.4
    ],
    "text": "livelihood.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      451.28,
      526.41,
      464.49
    ],
    "text": "3. The Appellant\u2019s mother is deceased, and his father is the only surviving parent,",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      471.1,
      209.16,
      484.14
    ],
    "text": "who is in ill health.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      490.9,
      458.69,
      504.11
    ],
    "text": "4. The Appellant bears the responsibility of caring for his ailing father.",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      522.7,
      526.14,
      535.74
    ],
    "text": "In the instant case, the said sentence or penalty prescribed by written law is found in",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      542.62,
      345.38,
      555.66
    ],
    "text": "Section 354 and Section 364 (2)(e) of the Penal Code;",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      574.42,
      315.72,
      587.46
    ],
    "text": "Section 354 of the Penal Code reads as follows,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      606.22,
      529.87,
      619.26
    ],
    "text": "\u201cWhoever kidnaps any person from Ceylon or from lawful guardianship shall be",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      626.14,
      529.88,
      639.18
    ],
    "text": "punished with imprisonment of either description for a term which may extend to",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      645.97,
      335.78,
      659.01
    ],
    "text": "seven years, and shall also be liable to fine\u201d",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      677.77,
      345.02,
      690.81
    ],
    "text": "Section 364 (2)(e) of the Penal Code reads as follows,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      709.69,
      188.33,
      722.73
    ],
    "text": "(2) \u201cWhoever\u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      781.3,
      324.77,
      805.78
    ],
    "text": "Page 4 of 6",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      71.91,
      529.8,
      84.95
    ],
    "text": "(e) commits rape on a woman under eighteen years of age; shall be punished with",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      91.73,
      529.96,
      104.77
    ],
    "text": "rigorous imprisonment for a term not test than ten years and not exceeding twenty",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      111.65,
      529.79,
      124.69
    ],
    "text": "years and with fine and shall in addition be ordered to pay compensation of an",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      131.45,
      529.87,
      144.49
    ],
    "text": "amount determined by court to the person in respect of whom the offence was",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      151.25,
      364.43,
      164.29
    ],
    "text": "committed for the injuries caused to such person;",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      183.05,
      529.82,
      196.09
    ],
    "text": "Provided, however, that where the offence is committed in respect of a person",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      202.97,
      529.84,
      216.01
    ],
    "text": "under sixteen years of age, the court may, where the offender is a person under",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      222.77,
      529.95,
      235.81
    ],
    "text": "eighteen years of age and the intercourse has been with the consent of the person,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      242.57,
      440.44,
      255.61
    ],
    "text": "impose a sentence of imprisonment for term less than ten years.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      274.52,
      526.3,
      287.56
    ],
    "text": "Our Courts have considered that when the Learned Trial Judge considers the mitigatory",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      294.32,
      526.31,
      307.36
    ],
    "text": "and aggravating factors, there is a duty cast on the Judge to give reasonable consideration",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      314.12,
      526.46,
      327.16
    ],
    "text": "to such factors. I am mindful that the starting point of the sentence for this rape is 10",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      334.04,
      105.69,
      347.08
    ],
    "text": "years.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      365.84,
      530.07,
      378.88
    ],
    "text": "His Lordship S.N. Silva J (as he was then) in the case of Attorney General v. Ranasinghe",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      71.31,
      385.64,
      526.36,
      398.68
    ],
    "text": "and Others (1993) 2 SLR 81 had referred to the judgment of Kieth Billiam (1986) Volume",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      405.44,
      526.2,
      418.48
    ],
    "text": "Criminal Appeal Report 347, where the Court had identified the following instances as",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      425.36,
      184.29,
      438.4
    ],
    "text": "aggravating features.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      457.18,
      320.81,
      470.22
    ],
    "text": "\u201c1. Violence is used to commit the rape.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      488.98,
      329.46,
      502.02
    ],
    "text": "2. A weapon is used to frighten the victim.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      520.9,
      214.99,
      533.94
    ],
    "text": "3. Rape is repeated.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      552.7,
      502.5,
      565.74
    ],
    "text": "4. The Defendant had a previous conviction of rape or other serious offences.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      584.5,
      345.52,
      597.54
    ],
    "text": "5. The victim is either very old or very young.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      616.3,
      529.85,
      629.34
    ],
    "text": "Further held that \u201cwhere any one or more aggravating factors are present, the",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      636.22,
      529.74,
      649.26
    ],
    "text": "sentence should be substantially higher than the figure suggested as the starting",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      656.05,
      148.4,
      669.09
    ],
    "text": "point.\u201d",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      681.85,
      526.33,
      694.89
    ],
    "text": "In the instant case, the starting point for sentencing in respect of the offence is ten years.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      701.77,
      526.36,
      714.81
    ],
    "text": "Thereafter, it is incumbent upon the Learned High Court Judge to exercise his discretion",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      721.57,
      526.47,
      734.61
    ],
    "text": "by striking a balance between the aggravating and mitigating factors relevant to the",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
